text: Kaneez is a Pakistani Urdu black and white movie directed by renown director Hassan Tariq and produced by Hassan Tariq and Ali Sufiyan Afaqi. It cast Waheed Murad, Zeba, Mohammad Ali, Sabiha Khanam, Lehri, Saqi, Adeeb and Talish. It is a musical family relationship movie. Waheed Murad and Zeba played lead roles, and Mohammad Ali played a complete character role. ==References== Category:1960s Pakistani movies Category:1965 movies
